        "details": {
            "description": "<p>This swirling column of glowing red light is enchanted with the unholy magic of the Devourer. Looking into its depths shows any creature the power of true devastation, filling them with longing and despair.</p>",
            "disable": "<p>@Check[athletics|dc:19] or @Check[medicine|dc:19] to revive an affected creature, @Check[occultism|dc:22] or @Check[performance|dc:22] to weave your own message into the projection, @Check[arcana|dc:24] or @Check[computers|dc:24] to disrupt the projections, or @Check[religion|dc:25] to invoke your deity for protection</p>",
